@node _stat_r
@section @code{_stat_r}---Reentrant version of stat
@findex _stat_r
@strong{Synopsis}
@example
#include <reent.h>
int _stat_r(struct _reent *@var{ptr},
    const char *@var{file}, struct stat *@var{pstat});

@end example
@strong{Description}@*
This is a reentrant version of @code{stat}.  It
takes a pointer to the global data block, which holds
@code{errno}.

